information: Sweet Ingredients is your advisory distributor for natural sweeteners as sugar substitutes and food additives, focusing on low-glycemic, tooth-friendly sugar substitutes, such as Xylitol. We offer you an extensive range of ingredients with added value. Special characteristics make each of our products very useful for reaching your objectives terms of both manufacturing and marketing. Our customers come from a wide range of areas in food manufacture (including producers of bakery goods, sweets and beverages), from the pharmaceutical and cosmetics sector and other industries.
